bookTitle: RISE HIGHER: 9 Steps for a woman to overcome any challenge, become the leader she deserves to be and do what she loves
Plot: Imagine if you had thousands of happy memories that light you up each day. And imagine if those memories are just multiplying each day. How would your life seem, any different from what it is now? In RISE Higher, multi-passionate Entrepreneur Aureen M. Monteiro walks you through the steps ambitious women are using to overcome challenges, become the leader they deserve to be, and do what they love every single day.
